### Listar Campos da Matriz
GET {{baseUrl}}/exames/matrizes/{matrizId}/campos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Atualizar Campo
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/exames/matrizes/{matrizId}/campos/{campoId}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "label": "Hemoglobina (Hb)",
  "valorReferenciaMin": 13.0,
  "valorReferenciaMax": 17.0
}

### Remover Campo
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/exames/matrizes/{matrizId}/campos/{campoId}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Reordenar Campos
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/exames/matrizes/{matrizId}/campos/reorder
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "campos": [
    { "campoId": "uuid-1", "ordemExibicao": 1 },
    { "campoId": "uuid-2", "ordemExibicao": 2 },
    { "campoId": "uuid-3", "ordemExibicao": 3 }
  ]
}
